{
  "title": "Festive Fiery Norwegian Cheese Casserole",
  "description": "A shojin-friendly Norwegian dish featuring fermented cheese, enchilada sauce, and confit-tomato, perfect for a festive gathering.",
  "cuisine": "Norwegian",
  "diet": [
    "vegetarian",
    "shojin"
